tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE vehicle_health_data (
    vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    engine_temperature FLOAT,
    oil_pressure FLOAT,
    tire_pressure FLOAT,
    last_maintenance_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceSchedule (
    schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    maintenance_type VARCHAR,
    scheduled_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY(vehicle_id) REFERENCES VehicleHealthData(vehicle_id)
);

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceSchedule (
    maintenance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    maintenance_date DATE,
    maintenance_type VARCHAR(50),
    technician_name VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceHistory (
    maintenance_history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    maintenance_id INT,
    vehicle_id INT,
    maintenance_date DATE,
    maintenance_type VARCHAR(50),
    parts_replaced VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceChecks (
    check_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    check_date DATE,
    check_type TEXT,
    check_result TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE VehicleHistory (
    history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    check_id INT,
    mechanic_id INT,
    repair_date DATE
);
